OL,7,MComing Soon - Teletext                 
OL,9,BIn my next video I will undertake an   
OL,10,Binvestigation of teletext. This is a   
OL,11,Bfascinating topic and I'll explain in  
OL,12,Bdetail how it works.                   
OL,13,FI've obtained some interesting         
OL,14,Fequipment to illustrate the story      
OL,15,Fincluding a broadcast teletext         
OL,16,Finserter, and a teletext add-on for the
OL,17,FBBC Micro Computer.                    
OL,18,EI'll also look at some novel uses for  
OL,19,Eteletext aside from the familiar       
OL,20,Emagazine services. And we'll look at   
OL,21,Ehow teletext is still in use today.    
OL,22,Q]MGvisit me onlineCretroworkshop.uk    
